Q10.   Write the python program to change the first item (22) of a list within the follwing tuple to 222.
              t1=(11,[22,33],44,55)
Ans.    t1=(11,[22,33],(2,4,16))
        t2=list(t1)
        t2[1][0]=222
        print(t2)                      
                       '''If we want to change the t2 value again in tuple we can t1=tuple(t2)'''
                       '''then we can find t1 value as in their first form'''
                       
                       
